Fʋ "browser" la pʋ tʋm nɛ uploadwizardɛ bɛɛ mɔr JavaScript ka li kpiis, alazug ti pa'annɛf nɛ gbaʋŋ linɛ ka na vɛ'ɛg kpɛn'ɛs. ([https

mwe-upwiz-tutorial-error-cannot-transfor: Gafara, ti pʋ nyɛ pa'alʋg la footo kanɛ mak zɛmis ka na si'al nindakaŋaa. Nɛ'ɛŋa tʋ'ʋn an yɛlbil bi'ela nɛ Wikimedia Commons; nya'aŋ fʋ ti maligim mɔ ya'as.

mwe-upwiz-flickr-disclaimer1: Gbaʋŋ kaŋa na vɛ'ɛg labaar linɛ ka flicker.com zaŋ la niŋ [https://www.flickr.com/help/terms/ terms of use] nɛ [https://www.flickr.com/help/privacy-policy/ privacy policy] ni.
mwe-upwiz-flickr-disclaimer2: Baŋim ye fʋn zaŋid laʋk kaŋa ye fʋ tʋm la,fʋ IP adɛris nɛ fʋ bɔɔdim labaar na bɛ flicker ni.

mwe-upwiz-multi-file-select2: Gaŋim faalnam banɛ ka fʋ na bɔɔd ye vɛ'ɛgi kpɛn'ɛsɛ. Gban'am "shift" la nɛ nu'ug ka din gaŋ faalnam bɛdegʋ nɔ'ɔr ayinne. Fʋ tʋn'e gaŋ bɛdegʋ ti paae $1 {{PLURAL:$1|file|files}} n vɛ'ɛgi kpɛn'ɛs.
